    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.37a.25"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">25</fw>
                
                <note>ans. 5/30/77</note>
                
                <fw type="imprint">
                    <hi rend="caps">FORT HAYS KANSAS STATE COLLEGE 
                        <lb/>
                    HAYS, KANSAS</hi> 67601
                        <lb/>
                    Department of History 
                        <lb/>
                    ________________________________________
                    <figure>
                        <figDesc>Fort Hays Kansas State College Seal</figDesc>
                        <p>FORT HAYS KANSAS STATE COLLEGE</p>
                    </figure> 
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>May 21, 1973</dateline>
                
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>5835 Vine St.</addrLine> 
                        <addrLine>Lincoln, Nebraska 68505</addrLine>
                    </address>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Many thanks to you and Mrs. Young for the wonderful visit we had last Saturday. I have long loved and respected your work, and the opportunity to visit you was an experience I shall treasure all my life. I'm sending under separate cover an autographed copy of something I wrote as a token of appreciation. Your kind remarks about my brief review of <hi rend="underline">All Is But a Beginning</hi> thrilled me no end. I look forward to the rest of the autobiography.</p>
                <closer>    
                    <salute>With best wishes for good health and good writing, I am,</salute>
                    <salute>Sincerely,</salute>
                
                    <signed>Leo E. Oliva</signed>
                    <signed>Leo E. Oliva</signed> 
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
